<paragraph id="0C5AE361FFA1FFBD15DBF8D7B7CDF8A4" blockId="10.[151,506,1842,1905]" box="[151,506,1878,1905]" pageId="10" pageNumber="235">Figs 1G–J, 2H, 3DE, 5D, 8A–I.</paragraph>
